  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "DIGITAL MARKETING MANAGER",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>We are seeking an experienced Digital Marketing Manager to drive our wholesale business growth through effective digital marketing strategies. The role focuses on B2B marketing, lead generation, brand visibility, and dealer/distributor engagement across digital platforms.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Develop and execute digital marketing strategies tailored for wholesale and B2B markets to accelerate business growth</li><li>Generate qualified leads targeting distributors, retailers, and bulk buyers to expand sales opportunities</li><li>Manage and optimize Google Ads, LinkedIn Ads, and Meta Ads campaigns for precise B2B audience targeting</li><li>Oversee company website content, product listings, and enquiry forms to enhance user engagement and lead capture</li><li>Lead social media management focused on trade promotions to increase brand visibility among dealers and distributors</li><li>Improve SEO performance for wholesale-related keywords and product categories to boost organic traffic</li><li>Track, analyze, and report on campaign performance and return on investment to inform strategic decisions</li><li>Collaborate closely with the sales team to convert digital leads into confirmed orders</li><li>Design and implement email marketing and WhatsApp campaigns to engage and retain dealer networks</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Bachelor’s degree in Marketing or a related field (preferred)</li><li>Proven experience in digital marketing within wholesale or B2B trade environments</li><li>Strong knowledge of lead generation and conversion strategies</li><li>Proficiency with Google Analytics, Google Ads, and Meta Business Suite</li><li>Understanding of distributor and reseller marketing dynamics</li><li>Excellent communication and analytical skills</li></ul>",
